        "Ingredients": "['1 lb. Chinese broccoli or broccolini, trimmed, cut in thirds crosswise', '¼ cup soy paste (such as Yu Ding Xing)']",
        "Instructions": "['Set a steamer basket in a large pot filled with 1\" water, cover pot, and bring water to a boil. Add broccoli to steamer basket, cover pot, and steam broccoli until crisp-tender, about 5 minutes.', 'Meanwhile, whisk soy paste and 2 Tbsp. water in a large bowl.', 'Arrange broccoli on a platter and drizzle sauce over.']",
